[metadata]
Name:Animate Dead Sacrifice On Leave
Goal:Win
Turns:6
Difficulty:Medium
Description:P0 has Animate Dead + Disenchant in hand and 4 City of Brass. P0's graveyard holds Triskelion. P0 casts Animate Dead to reanimate Triskelion (it returns under P0's control with three +1/+1 counters and -1/-0 from the Aura, a 3/4), then Disenchants its OWN Animate Dead. Per Animate Dead's Oracle ("When Animate Dead leaves the battlefield, that creature's controller sacrifices it") the reanimated Triskelion is sacrificed to its owner's graveyard (CR 603 delayed trigger; CR 701.17 sacrifice; CR 704.5 aura falls off when destroyed). Tracks mtg-400 / mtg-394.

